      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about expectations though. even if i was \"living up to them\" it wouldn't change the fact that the person doing the living isn't me. i'm just observing this thing that looks like me, talks like me, and does my job. if the real me is gone, then what is the point of keeping the shell going? it just feels like a huge, exhausting lie.",
